{"tid":111742,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"理大學生會一號候選內閣繫理Polymer基本上係政治投機派","createTime":"2017-02-07T15:14:17.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-18T09:27:29.000Z","uid":14090,"like":34,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"3eb80636241a25504b72d07f0a3ff8449507c209","tid":111742,"uid":14090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-07T15:14:17.000Z","msg":"繫理Polymer一向<strong>自稱本土</strong>，用本土個名上莊唔係問題，但佢地連本土最基本既理念都搞唔清，只係會搞臭本土個朵<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/vlzxsfbt\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fvlzxsfbt&h=371088c1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n來源：蕭雲facebook page<br />\n<br />\n上面證明左佢一直自稱本土派<br />\n<br />\n但佢地連最基本既本土理念都唔知係咩，就掛本土個名出黎，博人認同<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/9fmel4ao\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F9fmel4ao&h=5af511f6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n來源：蕭雲facebook page<br />\n<br />\n乜本土會支持一國兩際架咩? 我真係第一次見，一國既大前題下，本土就唔會存在，咁你講咩本土? 呢班人實際係大左膠<br />\n<br />\nOK，我地再睇睇政綱<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/iq708wob\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fiq708wob&h=0e8fb3d3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n依家又話自己民主自決派，民主自決定本土呀屌你老母，乜撚都唔識就拎人地個名黎幫自己宣傳<br />\n<br />\n係切切實實既<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">政治投機派</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n見今期興啲咩就用咩黎做政綱，我屌你老母<br />\n<br />\n利申返先，非poly學生，港獨<br />\n<br />\n屌你老母，最睇唔過眼呢啲垃圾大學生，為上莊而上莊，政治立場搞撚到亂哂，根本一班唔撚識野既MK仔上莊<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent-arn2-1.xx.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/16508733_821354661336814_6066777253622101083_n.jpg?oh=4ffd5c58e1c3b157a653d8f939c9dc38&amp;oe=5902E96D\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent-arn2-1.xx.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F16508733_821354661336814_6066777253622101083_n.jpg%3Foh%3D4ffd5c58e1c3b157a653d8f939c9dc38%26oe%3D5902E96D&h=f69789b9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n各位poly同學仔，認撚住呢三條MK粉皮，再呼籲你啲朋友同學唔好投比佢！！"},{"pid":"dc095dde10d317d4dba34fa8af1dea52dfa42c99","tid":111742,"uid":14090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-07T15:14:57.000Z","msg":"push! 呢個post會不定時推到投票日"},{"pid":"12add51dbf73d01039e366752d2e8397233adcdd","tid":111742,"uid":14090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-07T15:15:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>push! 呢個post會不定時推到投票日<span style=\"color: red;\">完</span></blockquote>"},{"pid":"c063028c176a52a1b0635ab5a0904d58ad4b449e","tid":111742,"uid":14090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-07T15:16:20.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e3a8c48698db9482402d1870bc50a5d627c418ff","tid":111742,"uid":14090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-07T15:17:18.000Z","msg":"垃圾"},{"pid":"98e519022777d4cf7d6914ccd6bbfd198c985007","tid":111742,"uid":14090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-07T15:18:14.000Z","msg":"垃圾莊"},{"pid":"a3673838475a14b02058bc1c2db18aa3da6e6c61","tid":111742,"uid":14090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-07T15:19:27.000Z","msg":"push!"},{"pid":"d851f6d573216bcc9db26246bdc45b45377e83bb","tid":111742,"uid":14090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-07T15:20:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d4fe53036adf6d4931c690605abd6bdec67dfbff","tid":111742,"uid":14090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-07T15:20:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8dfbb0d501ea1c7e59f0e620a8fdcd0708db50ac","tid":111742,"uid":14090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-07T15:25:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4dfc1bcc46a4f92b481f308e99dd4ff27e11732e","tid":111742,"uid":14090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-07T15:26:17.000Z","msg":"出黎講野啦 垃圾係到負評唔出聲"},{"pid":"25bc81c9e537fccba20c200cbd51b704361dd72e","tid":111742,"uid":58249,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-07T15:27:59.000Z","msg":"poly學生會每年除左派本簿之外 仲做過乜9？<br />\nwfc"},{"pid":"852ec8335763ed6d4e06c68551547240b37809d3","tid":111742,"uid":16970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-07T15:29:41.000Z","msg":"我又入嚟問下: 本土派係咪一定要支持獨立?"},{"pid":"e70125a31301f5e45a0b631dac040fa1f2b1c8e9","tid":111742,"uid":2128,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-07T15:30:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我又入嚟問下: 本土派係咪一定要支持獨立?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n同問"},{"pid":"54aa260c37cfeb0cc850d46cd4547a1c82dea9b4","tid":111742,"uid":14090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-07T15:34:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我又入嚟問下: 本土派係咪一定要支持獨立?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你自己上網睇下本土派係點先啦<br />\n<br />\n冇話一定支持獨立<br />\n<br />\n本土派有分港獨，城邦，歸英，民族自決(非民主自決)"},{"pid":"cc5b2ec0ecda534db8a33ff2ae213621ca663c59","tid":111742,"uid":14090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-07T15:35:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>poly學生會每年除左派本簿之外 仲做過乜9？<br />\nwfc</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咁好心佢地就唔好借本土個名呃莊上 自己打住本土旗號就唔該唔好一時本土一時民主自決"},{"pid":"ed82519f1c636b9abfca9ea39aac076b41489457","tid":111742,"uid":14090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-07T15:37:26.000Z","msg":"我重申一次，我從來冇要求過本土就一定支持獨立，但我最贂唔起呢班偽本土係到呃莊上，用本土個名黎自稱本土莊<br />\n<br />\n民主自決從來都唔屬於本土既 佢地係切切實實既政治投機派"},{"pid":"f31f89ddbc900fca74eda7512e8f0aebe0d01b4d","tid":111742,"uid":14090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-07T15:42:51.000Z","msg":"雖然到左2017，都唔要求學生會做到啲咩，唔再奢望學生會搞咩社會運動，根本到左呢個時候，任何野都唔應該再依賴學生會，佐我最睇唔起啲人係到收割光環<br />\n<br />\n邊一邊紅，就用邊一邊黎做政綱，政治投機派不得好死"},{"pid":"bb9ef04c5034d3766c413b0ea7d44b0d2928f784","tid":111742,"uid":14090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-07T15:43:09.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"213a151f4d948b8104c99c130d8e3ae4332d5da4","tid":111742,"uid":14090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-07T15:43:30.000Z","msg":"垃圾莊"},{"pid":"c62fa73e5bad478ae05a2168124b510496fcf5bf","tid":111742,"uid":14090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-07T15:44:57.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c7f8b81d3b85559b0ba9d7f6d2c760050af5e2e0","tid":111742,"uid":9677,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-07T15:46:24.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"47114536d2005c2444c3dece56b55881c9aecb8c","tid":111742,"uid":14090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-07T15:47:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>推</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f98ac4973478a9e62a3f96d5e30facb8b317233","tid":111742,"uid":14090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-07T15:47:59.000Z","msg":"PUSH"},{"pid":"7ccde2cd32713c2c03a95dc46c4a4a1de8cea921","tid":111742,"uid":14090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-07T15:49:32.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"90ffab58838abd70970e353ec7b8c2ae0c188c21","tid":111742,"uid":14090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-07T15:54:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6bd0a086bfdfc53d229eb571d7d6693b75bf9a2a","tid":111742,"uid":25421,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-07T15:58:37.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b485620e2e86d4c2b8b1cb0f898d56eda71184a7","tid":111742,"uid":14090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,